data.title: Certifications issued for Etimag Etiket Matbaacılık Ambalaj San. ve Tic. A.Ş.
data.meta_description: Overview of the certificates issued for Etimag Etiket Matbaacılık Ambalaj San. ve Tic. A.Ş. by DQS, a global provider of certification audits and assessments.
data.text: Production of packaging material as paper labels, security bands, self-adhesive labels, shrink sleeve label, OPP label, flexible label by using UV and solvent printing (Rotogravure, Flexo, offset) and sleeving of PET and glass bottles.
